des: Learn about upcoming events in Duvall, Washington. This Alexa skill reads upcoming event notices from a customized version of the Duvall Chamber of Commerce RSS feed. The customized feed is provided by chamber member, Tellus Consulting.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
